data.description: Explore all the possibilities this 38.7 acre property in Banks has to offer Close to Hwy 26 & 47, Banks/Vernonia Trailhead & 20 mins to Hillsboro/Intel. Relax on the large deck that overlooks the tree lined property. There is space for all your toys & horses in the 52x92 6 stall barn w/tack room. A 12x16 2-story shed is waiting for you turn it into a garden shed, she shed, etc. You'll be a part of the conversation while entertaining thanks to the open floor plan & large kitchen w/ss appliances.
data.whatILove: I love that the property is peaceful and perfect for a household of any size.  I appreciate the diverse uses for the property, and the space to store all of your toys including horses.  I love being outdoors so having the Banks/Vernonia trailhead so close to the home is a bonus.  I love the privacy that the property affords you while still having neighbors.  Being close to Hwy 26 makes commuting, going out to dinner, getting groceries and more easy.
